data.description: 4 year old starter home that is conveniently located near the city. This house features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, the primary bedroom sits on the first level and speaking of the first level this house has an open concept. The utility room is located inside which leads to the garage. This house has vinyl flooring throughout the first level with carpet in the bedrooms and the stairway. The second level features 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath. With a quick access to all major highways it will be a quick commute to work or school. Call your favorite realtor for a showing today!
